org.bonitasoft.engine.identity

Class ContactDataCreator

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.bonitasoft.engine.identity.ContactDataCreator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class ContactDataCreator
extends Object
implements Serializable
    Represents a helper for creating ContactData. Chaining is possible with this creator to ease the ContactData creation.
    For instance, new ContactDataCreator().setEmail("john.doe@bonitasoft.com").setPhoneNumber("012456789");
    Since:
    6.0.0
    Author:
    Matthieu Chaffotte, Celine Souchet
    See Also:
